  <p slot="paragraph">If you’re having problems with your boiler, like no heating or hot water, loss of water pressure might be to blame.</p>
  <p slot="paragraph">The good news is low boiler pressure is relatively easy to spot – and you can often put it right yourself. So, here’s our quick and easy guide to re-pressurising a boiler.</p>
